‚çù gpt.a+ - Mini-GPT: Multi-Head Transformer in Pure A+
‚çù First-ever GPT implemented entirely in A+!
‚çù 8-token vocab, 4-head attention, FFN, layer norm, residuals
‚çù Trained weights from Python; forward pass + self-test in A+

‚çù === Model Configuration ===
vocab‚Üê8
seq‚Üê4
dm‚Üê8
nheads‚Üê4
dk‚Üê2
dff‚Üê16

‚çù === Helper: Sigmoid ===
sigmoid{x}: {
  ‚éï 1√∑1+*-x
}

  ‚çù === Helper: Softmax (row-wise) ===
softmax{row;n}: {
  ‚çù Find max for numerical stability
  mx‚Üêrow[0]
  i‚Üê0
  while (i<n) {
    if (row[i]>mx) { mx‚Üêrow[i] }
    i‚Üêi+1
  }
  ‚çù Compute exp(x - max) and sum (store in temporary array)
  tmp‚Üên ‚ç¥ 0
  sm‚Üê0.0
  i‚Üê0
  while (i<n) {
    e‚Üê*row[i]-mx
    tmp[i]‚Üêe
    sm‚Üêsm+e
    i‚Üêi+1
  }
  ‚çù Normalize back into row
  i‚Üê0
  while (i<n) {
    row[i]‚Üêtmp[i]√∑sm
    i‚Üêi+1
  }
  row
}

